# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  .gitignore — keep the repo lean for cloud handoff.
#  KEEP: code, README, the game (SpaceHuggers-main/), and the CURRENT v2 model
#        (game_models_v2/ppo_sh_latest|best|bestlevel.zip).
#  DROP: archived/failed experiments, dated backups, rolling checkpoints,
#        TensorBoard logs, and regenerable visualization artifacts.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Archived experiments & dated backups (NOT needed to continue the work) ───
game_models_v2_farm_*/
game_models_v2_farm_exit_*/
